au.id.djc.rdftemplate.html

Class XHTMLEventConsumer

  • java.lang.Object
    • au.id.djc.rdftemplate.html.XHTMLEventConsumer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    XMLEventConsumer

    public class XHTMLEventConsumer
extends Object
implements XMLEventConsumer
    XMLEventConsumer implementation which indirects to another event consumer, but munges the stream on the way through to adhere to the vagaries of (X)HTML.

    Only elements in the XHTML namespace are modified, elements from other namespaces are passed through untouched.

    The HTML-specific things currently handled by this class are:

    • Nested anchors are removed (they are illegal)
